AD_REF_TABLE.WHERECLAUSE: EXISTS (SELECT * FROM C_BPartner bp WHERE AD_User.C_BPartner_ID=bp.C_BPartner_ID AND bp.IsSalesRep='Y')
M_Warehouse.AD_Client_ID=@#AD_Client_ID@ AND (select ad.isactive from ad_org ad where ad.ad_org_id = M_Warehouse.AD_Org_ID) = 'Y'
EXISTS (SELECT * FROM AD_Column c WHERE AD_Table.AD_Table_ID=c.AD_Table_ID AND c.ColumnName='Posted')
C_BPartner.IsVendor='Y' AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM M_Product_PO po WHERE C_BPartner.C_BPartner_ID=po.C_BPartner_ID)
EXISTS (SELECT * FROM C_PeriodControl pc WHERE C_Period.C_Period_ID=pc.C_Period_ID AND pc.PeriodStatus='O')

C_BPartner.IsEmployee='Y' AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM C_BPartner_Location l WHERE C_BPartner.C_BPartner_ID=l.C_BPartner_ID AND l.C_Location_ID IS NOT NULL) AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM AD_User u WHERE C_BPartner.C_BPartner_ID=u.C_BPartner_ID)
(EXISTS (SELECT * FROM C_BPartner bp WHERE AD_User.C_BPartner_ID=bp.C_BPartner_ID AND (bp.IsEmployee='Y')) OR AD_User.C_BPartner_ID IS NULL)
M_Product.M_Product_Category_ID IN (SELECT M_Product_Category_ID FROM M_Product_Category WHERE M_Product_Category.Em_Epcg_Israwmaterial='N')

AD_REF_TABLE.ORDERBYCLAUSE: Name, CASE WHEN (AD_Org_ID = @AD_Org_ID@) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END DESC

AD_REF_TABLE.WHERECLAUSE: M_Product.IsStocked='Y' AND M_Product.M_Product_Category_ID IN (SELECT M_Product_Category_ID FROM M_Product_Category WHERE M_Product_Category.Em_Epcg_Israwmaterial='Y')

M_Warehouse.AD_Client_ID=@#AD_Client_ID@ AND (select ad.isactive from ad_org ad where ad.ad_org_id = M_Warehouse.AD_Org_ID) = 'Y' AND M_Warehouse.M_Warehouse_ID IN (SELECT M_Warehouse_ID FROM EPCG_Warehouseuser DU WHERE @#AD_User_ID@ IN (SELECT AD_User_ID FROM EPCG_Warehouseuser WHERE EPCG_Warehouseuser.EPCG_Warehouseuser_ID=DU.EPCG_Warehouseuser_ID) )

C_DocType.AD_Client_ID=@#AD_Client_ID@ AND (@AD_Org_ID@ <> '0' OR COALESCE(@AD_Org_ID@,'-1')='-1') AND C_DocType.C_DocType_ID IN (SELECT C_DocType_ID FROM EPCG_Docuser DU WHERE @#AD_User_ID@ IN (SELECT AD_User_ID FROM EPCG_Docuser WHERE EPCG_Docuser.EPCG_Docuser_ID=DU.EPCG_Docuser_ID) )
M_Product.IsStocked='Y' AND M_Product.M_Product_Category_ID IN (SELECT M_Product_Category_ID FROM M_Product_Category WHERE M_Product_Category.Em_Epcg_Israwmaterial='N')
MA_SequenceProduct.MA_Sequence_ID = @MA_Sequence_ID@ AND MA_SequenceProduct.Productiontype = '-' AND MA_SequenceProduct.Line < TO_NUMBER(@Line@)
